+            :func:`fold_in`.
+        result (Tensor): The output tensor to fill in-place.
+        mean (float): Mean of the normal distribution. Default: ``0.0``.
+        std (float): Standard deviation of the normal distribution. Default: ``1.0``.
+
+    Returns:
